When Started Working on Story :::

1) move to  develop branch.

2) git pull ::: to take pull latest code...

3) git checkout -b feature/TRIBE-3658

After Making Changes for Story :::

1) git add .

2) git commit -m 'changes'

3) git push --set-upstream origin feature/TRIBE-3854  or git push --force
 
4) git checkout develop
 
5) git pull


Very Imp ::: For merging with current branch.

move to develop
git pull
 
move to tribe which needs to be deployed
git pull
 
git rebase develop

git push --force

If Conflicts Occurs :   

////// git add . 
///// git rebase --continue